# MISC::GET_ALLOCATED_STACK_SIZE

## Summary
Gets the size of the calling scripts allocated stack size

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Each script is an allocate stack of memory. This returns that value.
